         <abstract>
            <p>Text belonging to the magical and apocryphal literature, used by the <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/ETH1274Betaes">Beta ʾƎsrāʾel</persName> for liturgical purposes. 
               It is part of the readings prescribed for the Sabbath of Sabbaths and for initiation. The edition in <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/6BANA3I5"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Aescoly1951Recueil"/><title level="m">Recueil de textes falachas. Introduction. Textes éthiopiens. (édition critique et traduction). Index</title><title level="s">Travaux et mémoires de l’Institut d’ethnologie</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Aaron Zeev</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Aešcoly</t:surname></author><pubPlace>Paris</pubPlace><publisher>Institut d’ethnologie</publisher><date>1951</date><series><t:title xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" level="s">Travaux et mémoires de l’Institut d’ethnologie</t:title><t:biblScope xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" unit="volume">55</t:biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">55</biblScope><note type="url">https://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/bpt6k26168q.image</note></bibl> is based on <ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFabb107">BNFabb107</ref>.</p>
            
